column5: Can anyone give us an update on the current water temps in NW LS? Curious to learn how close the spawn might be, and how early, if at all, if might be this year.

I checked and the Middle of Lac is up to 7.5 C. The rivers are probably a bit warmer and I have heard report of walleye spawning now. So in a couple week the spawn should be over but that is up to mother nature.
